DESCRIPTION:\n\n\n\n\nPlease join us on the evening of Friday\, June 26\, for the Golden Crane Recognition Society Reception of the Behind the Shoji Summer Marketplace. Enjoy a first look at the unique selection of curated goods at our summer marketplace\, along with a delightful evening at the Garden.\n\n\n\nRSVP is required\; please contact developmentrsvp@japanesegarden.org to sign up.\n
