URL:https://japanesegarden.org/events/twilight-hours-2026-07-31/
SUMMARY:Twilight Hours 
DESCRIPTION:\n\nAs one of our most dedicated supporters\, Portland Japanese Garden is delighted to welcome you to our Twilight Hours event—a serene evening exclusively for our Tsubaki\, Matsu\, and Sakura Society members and their guests.  \n\nAs the gates close to the public\, the Garden enters a period of profound stillness. This event offers an opportunity to witness the landscape’s subtle shift from day to dusk\, allowing for a more intimate connection with the environment. Our premier Members will enjoy delightful music\, accompanied by refreshments and light appetizers. 
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://wpmedia.japanesegarden.org/w:1257/h:838/q:mauto/process:43701/id:4bc4fb0906ee494c79d842e46557e308/https://japanesegarden.org/TSell_Lantern_1.jpg
