SUMMARY:Phoenix Legacy Society Tea
DESCRIPTION:\nA tea bowl. Photo by Jonathan Ley.\n\n\n\nMembers of the Phoenix Legacy Society are invited to our annual event recognizing those who have committed to supporting the Garden through a bequest or future endowment. Invitations will be emailed to guests before the event.\n\n\n\nRSVP by August 6 to the Development team at developmentrsvp@japanesegarden.org.\n
